name: Kirigiri Kyoko Danganronpa
description:
A LoRA for Kirigiri Kyoko from Danganronpa. Trained on NAI with 118 pictures.

See samples for good prompts.

Best weight is around 0.8-1.0. Works on most of the anime based models like NAI, AOM3 or Anything v4.5.

I'm planning to do every danganronpa 1, 2 and V3 female characters, don't hesitate to tell me who you wants first.

All of my LoRAs will always be free. If you paid for this or an image using this LoRA, you got scamed! If you wants to supports me, feel free to buy me a Ko-Fi.
